descriptionHtml:
MANN+HUMMEL Connect is the central communications app of the MANN+HUMMEL Group, the leading global expert for filtration solutions.
The app provides the latest corporate and local news, and offers various services for the employees and partners – all in one place.
Connect, inform, engage: we invite our employees to be a vital part of the MANN+HUMMEL Community - anywhere, anytime, any device.
